        "class": "ital",
        "text": "But before all these ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Before the appearing of the false Christs — before the rumours of wars — the earthquakes, famines, and pestilences that were to be in divers places; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "they shall lay their hands on you, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "&c. — “How fully the particulars foretold in this verse were accomplished, we learn from the Roman historians, Tacitus and Suetonius, who have given an account of the persecution raised against the Christians by Nero. But the history of the Acts will throw the greatest light on this passage. For there we are told, that immediately after our Lord’s ascension, Peter and John were called before the Jewish senate, and beaten; (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 4:6-7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 5:40",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ";) that Stephen was brought before the same court; (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 6:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ";) and put to death; (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 7:58",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ";) that ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Saul made havoc of the church, entering into every house, and haling men and women, committed them to prison; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 8:3",
        "children": []
